title: Natas Kaupas for Lakai Echelon
description:
Lakai has partnered with the legendary Natas Kaupas on a limited edition Echelon collection.

The Natas Echelon collection includes three water-resistant Camby colorways with nautical flag details on the inside heel of the shoe. 

The Natas Echelon collection is available now at Lakai retailers

Filmed by: Roger Bagley
Edited by: Aaron Meza
